headline: KeyBanc Lifts Target on Expand Energy, Sees Cash Return Shift and Strong ROE Path
summary: KeyBanc Capital Markets raised its price target on Expand Energy (NASDAQ:EXE) from $130 to $135 on June 13 and kept the Overweight rating in place. The move comes as the firm’s analyst points to what they call a “cash return inflection point” for the company. It’s the shift that, according to the analyst, could reframe […]
